page.title: 14Home life in Seisdon
page.content: I live at Long Acre.At the back of our house is a field with cows in.I have a room of my own and I have got a double bed. I have one brother. We have a puppy and a bitch black coated retriever. They like playing with the cat.Every day I get up at 7 o/clock, have my wash then get changed and have breakfast before going to school.My favourite subject is Maths. My hobbies are reading,horse riding,and swimming. My favourite pop group are Duran Duran. I help my mum in the kitchen a lot and my brother helps Dad in the garden.I go to bed at 9 o/clock usually but at weekends it varies. I play with Joanna at weekends and on school nights I play with my friend Fiona.The playing fields are opposite my house.My Dad makes bikes like racers and BMX styles.My mum is a teacher. Granny and grandpa live in Wales.
